    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301510/extras/3c247acacbec4d44256a31914c50bf34.avif?t=1764765650\" width=960 height=102 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We’re currently in <strong>Kickstarter prelaunch</strong>, grinding our way up the ladder to reach the <i>Projects We Love</i> section. You can help just by <strong>hitting the &quot;Notify Me&quot; button</strong>! It’s free and makes a HUGE difference 🔔❤️</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>CHECK OUR WEBSITE FOR THE KICKSTARTER LINK </strong>👉</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kickstarter </strong>Backers will get:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✨ Play the <strong>closed pre-alpha almost a year early</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💸 Get the <strong>full-game at a discount</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⛩️ Unlock a <strong>Kickstarter-only prequel </strong>set 800 years before the main story</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎁 Access <strong>Kickstarter</strong> <strong>exclusive rewards </strong>and <strong>collectibles</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301510/extras/7473098fa2aa3e53e3cbc7714daeaf48.avif?t=1764765650\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301510/extras_big/7473098fa2aa3e53e3cbc7714daeaf48.avif?t=1764765650 width=800 height=302 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the <strong>Endless Blue</strong>, an ocean realm inhabited by mysterious creatures known as the <strong>Tomo</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A world both unknown and strangely nostalgic, where <strong><i>sandbox creativity</i></strong>, <strong><i>monster-taming</i></strong>, and <strong><i>multiplayer exploration </i></strong>come together in an <strong>open-world voxel RPG</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301510/extras/9ebbfdd7ec040702443d9447bee0ce41.poster.avif?t=1764765650\" width=700 height=358 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301510/extras/9ebbfdd7ec040702443d9447bee0ce41.webm?t=1764765650\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301510/extras/4e6004c96f0103c9e58e6e80a414a0fb.avif?t=1764765650\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301510/extras_big/4e6004c96f0103c9e58e6e80a414a0fb.avif?t=1764765650 width=800 height=339 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301510/extras/f0acecae5a1da275caa6bf5a9056ba60.avif?t=1764765650\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301510/extras_big/f0acecae5a1da275caa6bf5a9056ba60.webp?t=1764765650 width=1560 height=1979 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Moddable</strong> – Our intention is to keep it all open, so you can go ahead and break the game. If your dream is to replace all Tomo creatures with handsome pigeons playing illegal poker hands, then so be it. The world is your oyster!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301510/extras/2969419100c9bf63e93cd5c2389e29f1.poster.avif?t=1764765650\" width=700 height=394 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301510/extras/2969419100c9bf63e93cd5c2389e29f1.webm?t=1764765650\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301510/extras/ca85d5bdd2830f9b986c3b1fd81972d3.avif?t=1764765650\" width=1560 height=650 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join our <strong>Discord</strong> to keep up with us!<br></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>*Disclaimer:</strong> These screenshots showcase our pre-alpha build, where we're focusing on crafting engaging gameplay before bringing in the full visual experience later in development. For the best glimpse of our intended final look and feel, check out the trailer!</i><br><br><br><br><br><i>The game is still in early development and features may evolve, join our Discord to share your thoughts and help shape the roadmap!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>There is no public demo/beta currently available. Do NOT download any files from people claiming to be Onibi staff.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
